snippet.title: A Purrtato Tail - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist A Purrtato Tail now on Steam! http://bit.ly/PurrtatoOnSteam
Join our community on Discord! http://discord.gg/PurrtatoTail

Hope. Hope is different for everyone - regardless of if you are a human, or a potato cat living on the Isle of Moar.

A puzzle metroidvania about collecting vegetable cats and using their abilities to save the world. Coming 2019 to Steam, GameJolt, itch.io, PlayStation 4, and Xbox One.
